<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,
    maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="../css/show.css">
    <title>玩家展示</title>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <a id="back" class="back"><img src="../images/back.png"></a>
    <h3>查看身份</h3>
    <a id="close"><img src="../images/close.png"></a>
</header>
<main>
    <div class="sid">
        <span id="number">1</span>
    </div>
    <div class="show">
        <div class="pic" id="show1">
            <img src="../images/player1.png">
        </div>
        <div class="pic" id="show2" style="display:none">
            <div class="show-img">
                <img class="show_img" src="../images/player2.png">
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <p class="p1">角色：<span id="role">杀手</span></p>
                <p class="p2">词组：西伯利亚</p>
                <p class="p3">想办法猜到别人的词，同时还要注意不要暴露自己哦！</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="btn" id="btn">查看1号身份</div>
</main>
<script src="../js/show.js"></script>
</body>
</html>